'''Taẓɣlasmussut''' (zɣ [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]] : Thermique ''Taẓɣlant'' + Dynamique ''Tasmussut'') nɣ '''Tatirmudinamikt''' (s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]] : thermodynamic) tga yat ɣ igran n tasngama nɣ tafizikt nna isawaln f tirɣi d twuri d ddaraja n trɣi d tzdayt nns d tẓḍaṛt d uẓnẓṛ d tɣawsiwin yaḍnin izdin d [[tamtta|tmtta]].

Tiɣawsiwin ad ar ḍfarn kkuẓ ilugann n tatirmudinamikt nna as yakkan yan uglam asmktay, nẓḍar ad tn nfssr s tamikanikt n usidn. Ar nsxdam tatirmudinamikt ɣ kigan n igran ɣ tussniwin d timassanin, slawan akk ɣ [[takimit]] d [[Tasengama|tafizikt]] d utwal n tkimit d utwal n tfizikt, d igran yaḍnin zun d tasnzwit.

